{"tid":1221807,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位做咩都好，唔好亂犧牲自己","createTime":"2019-06-14T09:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T18:44:21.000Z","uid":90601,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e1323860dd3a78a2e8c9895674bb217a6282fe0e","tid":1221807,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"我係80後，由反國教已上街遊行，佔鐘佔銅佔旺都有去。五年前，我好感受到一件事，就係我地80後、90後依一代人，其實好多人都有心，目標就係要拎番「屬於我地既香港」，但係，我亦同時感受到另一件事，就係：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>要成就依一件事，單靠一兩代人，係絕對唔夠。</strong><br />\n<br />\n我今年已經30出頭，過左5年又再跑物資，又再同速龍玩捉依因，第二日仲要番工養家，體力真係唔係幾頂得順。今次見到咁多00後走出黎，仲分分鐘勇過我地依一代，有你地一齊撐住，我內心真係好感動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所以，你地更加唔可以隨便犧牲。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>做咩都好，唔好俾人拉，唔好死。</strong><br />\n<br />\n可能我唔係十八廿二，凡事總係往最壞既情況去諗。無論出面點轉風向，班建制點樣互射，有一個事實係唔會變：<strong>中共同香港係一個極權政府。</strong><br />\n<br />\n咩係極權？就係掌權者既決定，係無人可以反對同推翻，就係做錯決定都無所謂，無人可以阻止。<br />\n<br />\n今日如果維尼同777下令血腥清場，再硬過條例，可能美國會制裁，可能香港樓市會仆街，全世界屌柒佢地屠殺人民，但係對佢地係<strong>無損失</strong>。更加可怕既係，無人有能力阻止佢地，中共常委無，軍警無，建制無，基督教徒都無。<br />\n<br />\n我唔會叫大家做啲咩，或者唔好做啲咩，就當我係危言聳聽，如果真係見到大殺傷力既清場方式，唔好硬碰，走！唔好諗住「殺我呀屌你老母！我睇香港第日會點」，唔好理，走！<br />\n<br />\n你地係平民，對面係有武力既極權；你地手無寸鐵，而對面開完槍係唔洗有後果。生命無大家想象中咁堅強，唔好因為情緒而莽撞；黑警一定會用盡方法拉人，唔好有證據俾人周到。<br />\n<br />\n今次係香港史上最浩大，最有效率既反建制抗爭，但始終<strong>只係針對一條修訂條例</strong>，成功或唔成功，都絕唔會係終局之戰，咩新區旗、新國歌亦唔可能突然得到國際認可。幾時先係Endgame？大家心知肚明，未來民主新時代始終會企起身，但好難係短期之內。<br />\n<br />\n我無咁叻，唔識做預言家，只知好可能係長期抗爭，<strong>唔鬥長命，係鬥唔贏。未來要靠更多新生代，90後、00後、甚至10後</strong>。無論如何，一定唔好犧牲自己，一定要保住自己，先可以繼續同依個極權周旋落去。<br />\n<br />\n一個人俾人拉左，就可能少一個前線，可能少一個文宣，可能少一個急救，可能少一個經濟能力來源，抗爭力道又係再變細。<br />\n<br />\n我見到612好難過，亦好振奮，唔係因為我冷血，而係你見到在場既80後、90後、00後既行動能力係勁撚到癲！call物資、打手勢，後面support前面，避tear gas打遊擊，就咁已經頂到幾個鐘。如果唔係對家有全副武裝，我深信佢地無能力清場。一直以黎好多人笑你地無用，考DSE，玩抖音，但我真心覺得未來香港可以交俾你地，老屎忽先係阻止你地個地球轉。<br />\n<br />\n我更深信只要大家繼續團結，終有一日，大家會搵到新天新地。<br />\n<br />\n我不厭其煩講多次，<strong>唔好犧牲自己，唔好俾人拉，唔好死。</strong><br />\n<br />\n或者所有行為都有代價，但香港人絕對值得擁有平等、自由同民主。<br />\n<br />\n撐落去，過程中或者你要面對失敗、無助、沮喪，但總有一日，你會為依片土地而驕傲。<br />\n<br />\n撐落去。天佑香港。"},{"pid":"d4b4e26b2ad02e351f28c3fdfdeff3c30e9eb82e","tid":1221807,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:59:17.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"5580ab2728f965899b836ba78d80ecd55db9b6a9","tid":1221807,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:59:45.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308117a5a45135e707dd4dc827a2fe746039eaf8","tid":1221807,"uid":1295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好有同感"},{"pid":"d870fff87ef4af492b69cf59b01d6f749bf88904","tid":1221807,"uid":182655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b8c07d99090fd58cb17fe3ff86091c15c9267a","tid":1221807,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"情況差唔多<br />\n命仔要緊, 我地仲需要多1-2代去壯大自己<br />\n無論今次最後成唔成功都好, 唔好比個社會食左你<br />\n國際舞台轉變緊, 香港會出現屬於我地既希望"},{"pid":"5fcf48e734bf99b394b7bffef99786ad8df5cd1b","tid":1221807,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"集氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fabd80fa36d0028dd996089396c6eaae572831a","tid":1221807,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d01752cc31e4a71df17da674b1d1e9af793551b","tid":1221807,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa0207da7e9cee2e8d65ba103922e3c7970bb98","tid":1221807,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ad38052d5b4dfdbd00ba425252557db47a7840","tid":1221807,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddfcaa884005ea185ff7ad8d9729422c78ff592","tid":1221807,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"天佑香港"},{"pid":"b16929af7040d2f31a07d74bed970707899d2674","tid":1221807,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:09:32.000Z","msg":"原來只係過左16日<br />\n依家睇番自己寫既野 諗起已經不在人世既三位同路人<br />\n我只係覺得欲哭無語<br />\n錯既唔係我地 要道歉既唔係我地 要付出代價既亦唔係我地<br />\n<br />\n堅持下去 有你有我<br />\n未來既香港仲需要大家<br />\n不被捕不流血<br />\n不氣餒不灰心<br />\n路好難行 但唔好離開 一定要行落去"},{"pid":"5115971a4c9eccd31a55d8393f6b15c983e97f1f","tid":1221807,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb935cc82cad70d916b0ae27d58ea784221dba97","tid":1221807,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝福各位 共勉之 71見"},{"pid":"2a77b615730af621560454f2721b4b41d689e93a","tid":1221807,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:38:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe97c68063f07fccdab94a59b20fa9f35f9ac640","tid":1221807,"uid":225144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:41:38.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一開吹水區，已經見到無數既post都係關於想尋死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n各位巴絲真係唔好諗咁多呀，我同大家一樣都好失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n如果你地真係好頂唔順既，不如入來呢個tg gp，我<br />\n地一齊面對啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/KVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpBqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=1f074f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/KVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg</a>"},{"pid":"2f5515cf6b12611ba780ec5d537391cf97c27302","tid":1221807,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:44:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}